# CAN-to-Ethernet Server for generic Interfaces (CAN API V3)

Copyright &copy; 2008 by Uwe Vogt, UV Software, Friedrichshafen \
Copyright &copy; 2012-2025 by Uwe Vogt, UV Software, Berlin (info@uv-software.com)

## Utility program `can_port`

`can_port` is a command line tool designed to open a network socket for CAN-to-Ethernet communication.
It connects to a CAN device and handles the data exchange between the CAN bus and local or remote clients. 

## CAN Interface API, Version 3

**CAN API V3** is a wrapper specification by UV Software to have a uniform CAN Interface API for various CAN interfaces from different vendors running under multiple operating systems.

## Git repo `can_port`

This repo only contains the source code for the utility program `can_port` to be integrated into CAN API V3 wrapper implementations as a git submodule.

